<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Đăng ký thành người quản lý</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 106vh;
        }
        .form-container, .message-container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        .form-container {
            margin-right: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        input[type="text"], input[type="date"], input[type="tel"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
        }
        .alert {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            display: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="form-container">
            <h1>Đăng ký</h1>
            <form id="registrationForm" action="register/manager/approve " method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="fullName">Họ tên</label>
                    <input type="text" id="fullName" name="fullName" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="birthDate">Ngày sinh</label>
                    <input type="date" id="birthDate" name="birthDate" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="address">Địa chỉ</label>
                    <input type="text" id="address" name="address" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="phone">Số điện thoại</label>
                    <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="idCard">Số căn cước</label>
                    <input type="text" id="idCard" name="idCard" required>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn">Đăng ký</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div id="message" class="message-container alert">
            Đơn của bạn đang chờ phê duyệt, chúng tôi sẽ cung cấp tài khoản admin cho bạn nếu đơn của bạn được duyệt thành công. Xin cảm ơn !!
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('registrationForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {
            event.preventDefault();
            document.getElementById('message').style.display = 'block';
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
